{"tid":1558631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有時間傾9.11割唔割不如用傾9.15遊行好過啦","createTime":"2019-09-10T13:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T14:05:45.000Z","uid":16007,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b07dcee2fd26d77bc03188150486b281072d0649","tid":1558631,"uid":16007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:57:45.000Z","msg":"支那幾句無成本9up就搞到咁多位手足係度長篇大論割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家都知隨機殺人呢D野一定唔會手足做，而家割左係咪就可以避免件事發生同對家老屈? 中共咪又係會不停拉埋一齊黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係中共就每日就話你地女姦男殺，等你地日日哂時間無時間宣傳行動，星期六日唔夠人出黎就會大條道理話社會已經平靜下來，慢慢黎個大清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我問幾個和理非朋友都話唔知9.15有民陣遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集中文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期日再現百萬大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4afb1fe71497123abe4b5af4fcb9d4fbb09db2","tid":1558631,"uid":16007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"209509649469166ffe30c84acf3ce7fb059f6875","tid":1558631,"uid":16007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"9d850a7d229aa80c2f243835839bd919d80ac412","tid":1558631,"uid":16007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:59:10.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"4a8ab089c6524094352f03f7f69825a0e92313ba","tid":1558631,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"edee016a6f3be774d1b7b19254406c6d3afd925d","tid":1558631,"uid":16007,"like":0,"dislik